  "detailed_description": "<br><br><br><strong>RCPG</strong> is a fast paced arcade combat-racing game, where you can drive remote controlled cars through tracks. fun obstacles ,combat abilities, maneuverability and boost.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>7 championship trophies in single player mode(Solo or Vs local player)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 different environment includes 6 tracks to play</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 cars</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 unique weapons, Rockets, Mine, Oil Trap</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 players split-screen multiplayer</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time trials</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>local leaderboard</li></ul><br>Keyboard, gamepad and joysticks are supported",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><br><strong>RCPG</strong> is a fast paced arcade combat-racing game, where you can drive remote controlled cars through tracks. fun obstacles ,combat abilities, maneuverability and boost.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>7 championship trophies in single player mode(Solo or Vs local player)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 different environment includes 6 tracks to play</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 cars</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 unique weapons, Rockets, Mine, Oil Trap</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 players split-screen multiplayer</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time trials</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>local leaderboard</li></ul><br>Keyboard, gamepad and joysticks are supported",
